modules.description: This module provides functions to parse strings, channels, and files into a result type using a generated parser, while producing detailed error messages with location information. It works with token and result types defined by the input parser module. Use this to simplify parsing workflows and improve error diagnostics when parsing source code.

This module simplifies parsing by providing functions to parse strings, channels, and files using a generated parser, producing detailed error messages with location information. It works with token and result types from the input parser module. Use it to streamline parsing workflows and improve error diagnostics when processing source code.
